item.title: CVE-2023-0145|2023-03-20T15:52:12.480Z -- unknown -- saan%20world%20clock
item.description: The Saan World Clock WordPress plugin through 1.8 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
